code: export var saveToStorage=function saveToStorage(name,data){if(!window||!window.localStorage){return;}window.localStorage.setItem(name,JSON.stringify(data));};export var getFromStorage=function getFromStorage(name){if(!window||!window.localStorage){return null;}try{return JSON.parse(window.localStorage.getItem(name));}catch(e){console.log(e);return null;}};
